    <item>
      <title>美国经济：制造业活动自 2022 年以来首次扩张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/us-economy-manufacturing-activity-expands-for-first-time-since-2022</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国 12 月工厂活动自 2022 年以来首次扩张，美国供应管理协会 (ISM) 制造业指数 1 月上涨 1.7 点至 50.9，创 2022 年 9 月以来最高水平。Michael McKee 对这些数字进行了分析。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/us-economy-manufacturing-activity-expands-for-first-time-since-2022</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 15:24:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥财政部长告诉投资者墨西哥可以承受关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/mexico-s-finance-chief-tells-investors-it-can-withstand-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥财政部长表示，墨西哥已采取措施保护其经济免受美国关税冲击，并且各部门正在共同努力，以防货币市场的流动性受到影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/mexico-s-finance-chief-tells-investors-it-can-withstand-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 15:01:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管受到美国征税，倍耐力仍致力于实现减债目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/pirelli-aims-to-stick-with-debt-reduction-goal-despite-us-levies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，尽管美国即将实施的关税威胁到这家意大利轮胎制造商的北美业务，但倍耐力公司预计今年仍将坚持其债务削减目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/pirelli-aims-to-stick-with-debt-reduction-goal-despite-us-levies</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 14:54:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>先锋集团的平均费用在经历史上最大降幅后降至 0.07%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/vanguard-s-average-fee-is-now-just-0-07-after-biggest-ever-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[先锋集团 (Vanguard Group) 已大幅削减数十只共同基金和 ETF 的费用，这一创纪录举措可能会给资产管理行业带来冲击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/vanguard-s-average-fee-is-now-just-0-07-after-biggest-ever-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 14:28:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士宝盛首席执行官的首次战略举措因 Benko 宿醉而受阻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/swiss-regulator-opens-proceedings-against-julius-baer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士宝盛集团有限公司 (Julius Baer Group Ltd.) 上个月聘请斯蒂芬·博林格 (Stefan Bollinger) 来结束因向破产的房地产集团提供贷款而造成的惨痛损失。但正是这段过去毁掉了这位新任首席执行官首次战略举措的展示。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/swiss-regulator-opens-proceedings-against-julius-baer</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 12:03:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希腊圣托里尼旅游中心进入地震高度警戒状态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/greek-tourist-hub-of-santorini-on-high-earthquake-alert</link>
      <description><![CDATA[过去两天，希腊圣托里尼岛发生多起小地震，当地政府发布高度警戒，警惕大地震，岛上学校停课，不鼓励公众集会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/greek-tourist-hub-of-santorini-on-high-earthquake-alert</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 10:16:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金属价格缩减跌幅，因交易员权衡特朗普关税范围</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/iron-ore-drops-as-trump-tariffs-raise-global-growth-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于围绕特朗普总统对中国、加拿大和墨西哥征收关税的范围以及对全球经济增长的影响存在不确定性，从铜到铝等工业金属价格缩减了早盘的跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/iron-ore-drops-as-trump-tariffs-raise-global-growth-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 00:57:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税引发避险需求，金价创下新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/gold-edges-higher-as-trump-tariffs-unsettle-global-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对加拿大、墨西哥和中国征收关税，并威胁对欧盟采取同样的措施后，投资者纷纷转向避险资产，黄金价格创下历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/gold-edges-higher-as-trump-tariffs-unsettle-global-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 23:08:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对美国最大原油供应国征收关税，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-3</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价上涨，因总统唐纳德·特朗普对美国两大原油供应国加拿大和墨西哥征收进口关税，威胁到美国消费者的成本上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-3</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 23:03:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税恐慌导致美元上涨，股市受创：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/dollar-surges-stocks-set-to-fall-on-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心美国大规模关税可能阻碍全球经济增长并加剧通胀，股市遭受重创，美元上涨，短期美国国债收益率表现出色。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/dollar-surges-stocks-set-to-fall-on-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 22:25:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
